1000
01:12:37,920 --> 01:12:40,480
- Yes, yes. What's your name?
- Petrescu.

1001
01:12:40,680 --> 01:12:42,238
- Petrescu?
- George Petrescu.

1002
01:12:42,560 --> 01:12:44,357
George... hold on.

1003
01:12:47,240 --> 01:12:49,071
Petrescu George.

1004
01:12:50,800 --> 01:12:51,835
Yes.

1005
01:12:55,240 --> 01:12:57,470
You donated on the 17th,

1006
01:12:58,360 --> 01:12:59,873
but we don't owe you anything.

1007
01:13:01,120 --> 01:13:02,473
But I donated.

1008
01:13:02,680 --> 01:13:05,638
Yes, that's true, you donated,
