got the wife all pissed at me...

1047
01:15:52,840 --> 01:15:54,592
Police! Call the police!

1048
01:16:29,360 --> 01:16:31,351
The sperm of Danish students, you say?

1049
01:16:31,880 --> 01:16:34,189
Yes, that's what the doctor said.

1050
01:16:34,560 --> 01:16:36,630
Well if I'd known,
I should have dyed my hair blond.

1051
01:16:40,920 --> 01:16:43,718
We should have gone to Michael's concert.

1052
01:16:46,160 --> 01:16:48,276
