1055
01:17:02,120 --> 01:17:04,475
He'll laugh in our face.

1056
01:17:05,440 --> 01:17:09,479
"You made fools of
yourselves in Bucharest."

1057
01:17:10,520 --> 01:17:12,112
"I'm going to fire all of you."

1058
01:17:35,760 --> 01:17:38,479
- What's wrong with you?
- Nothing.

1059
01:17:38,840 --> 01:17:41,115
Yeah, nothing. Tell me what's wrong?

1060
01:17:45,600 --> 01:17:47,636
