1067
01:18:27,440 --> 01:18:29,635
Come on, or we'll miss our train.

1068
01:18:32,480 --> 01:18:38,430
Our paths might cross someday.

1069
01:18:39,960 --> 01:18:47,071
Our paths and love,
Our thoughts and happiness.

1070
01:19:19,760 --> 01:19:21,990
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

1071
01:19:32,040 --> 01:19:32,995
